CustomField.description: Number of days between the JOA Open and the JOA Closed Dates. Zero if negative or missing dates.
CustomField.formula: IF(IF( Announcement_Close_Date__c - Announcement_Open_Date__c <0,NULL,Announcement_Close_Date__c - Announcement_Open_Date__c)> 999, NULL, IF( Announcement_Close_Date__c - Announcement_Open_Date__c <0,NULL,Announcement_Close_Date__c - Announcement_Open_Date__c))
CustomField.label: # Days JOA Open
